    title: "Iron Yard- Grok",
    description: "Greenville Grok is the event that we've always wanted to attend, with a focus on real conversations with real creative professionals."
  })

block content
  +navigation({
    title: 'Greenville Grok',
    color: 'red-orange'
  })

  .container
    .row
      .col-md-8
        h3 Get ready for Grok 2014
        p This year is going to be special for Grok. In addition to the amazing 10/20 conversations that we’re known for, attendees will get to drive BMWs on a racetrack and hear inspiring talks from keynote speakers. Here are links to where and what’s happening this year:
        ul
          li <a href="https://tagboard.com/grok14">Follow along via Tagboard</a>
          li <a href="#location">Location</a>
          li <a href="#schedule">Schedule</a>        
          li <a href="#speakers">Speakers</a>
          li <a href="#travel">Getting to Greenville</a>
        p Need to get in touch? Reach out to us on <a href="http://eepurl.com/QSmpn">Gather</a>. You can also ping <a href="http://twitter.com/greenvillegrok">@GreenvilleGrok</a> or <a href="mailto:grok@theironyard.com">grok@theironyard.com</a>
        hr 
        p Excited? We are too. We’ll see you in a few weeks. Until then, watch our video from last year and count the days.
        <iframe src="//player.vimeo.com/video/69313375" width="630px" height="354px" webkitallowfullscreen mozallowfullscreen allowfullscreen></iframe> 
        hr
        h3#location Location
        p This year we’re gathering at Certus Loft, a gorgeous loft in the historic Huguenot Mill. Here is the address:
