        hr
        h3#speakers Speakers
        p 
          | <strong>Sam Fogarino</strong>- <em>Interpol</em><br><br>
          | Sam is the drummer for Interpol and has worked on several other widely respected projects. He will be talking about ego and the process of creativity.<br><br>
          | <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sam_Fogarino"> Learn More</a>
        p 
          | <strong>Kristian Andersen</strong>- <em>KA+A</em><br><br>
          | Founder of an award-winning design firm, successful entrepreneur, angel and VC investor, and father of 5 kids, Kristian is going to talk about the meaning of success.<br><br>
          | <a href="http://www.kristian.vc/"> Learn More</a>
        hr
        h3#travel Getting To Greenville
        p Hop in a car and <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/Greenville,+SC/@34.8331685,-82.3628304,13z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m2!3m1!1s0x88578f6662fa1105:0xd8aa9d77bf257696">head our way</a> or fly into our beautiful <a href="http://www.gspairport.com/">international airport</a>.
